  "commit_message": "test(hook): serialize hook.bats to fix flaky auto-activate timeout\n\nThe interactive auto-activation tests in hook.bats drive real `flox\nactivate` runs through `expect`, and several build and activate two or\nthree environments in a single test. Run in parallel within the file\n(`bats --jobs`), they contend on the shared Nix store and pile up\nconcurrent executive (activation daemon) processes, which can starve an\nactivation long enough to blow past the 60s `expect` timeout. Because the\nexpect scrip",
